-- Insert default subscription tiers
INSERT INTO subscription_tiers (name, description, priceMonthly, priceYearly, maxStrategies, maxBrokerConnections, autoExecuteAllowed, prioritySupport) VALUES

('Pro', 'Full access with auto-execution capability', 9900, 99000, NULL, 3, TRUE, FALSE),
('Enterprise', 'Unlimited access with priority support', 29900, 299000, NULL, 10, TRUE, TRUE)
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE name = name;
